video_title: Change Is Growth! Happy Birthday To The One & Only Selena Gomez #selenagomez #jayshetty
transcript:
I hate change I really do but I felt in
the past year I have really really
embraced
on the uncomfortableness of change and I
think it's because I get so exhausted of
the same thing over and over again it
scares me but I did learn that my world
can be bigger it just becomes addicting
to to want to put yourself in these
situations and see what happens
